C. CAROLAE, C. F. dos Passos and L. P. Grey; J. D. Gunder Collection Ac. 34998; 
<typeStatus id="54EE88727B24FFBBFC5EFC13FB9BDBCD" box="[1010,1125,963,987]" pageId="22" pageNumber="21">Holotype</typeStatus>
